\# Lore

Some pages will have lore bits sprinkled throughout. English is not my native
tongue, so writing in a more archaic-sounding style comes difficult to me, but
I'm doing my best. That is, some of the lore snippets might sound utterly
meaningless, although I guess that's half the vibe.

\# Webrings

I'm not part of a ton of \link{webring \label webrings}, but oh well.

