\## Source Code

\link{nihil \label The source} for this site's static site generator is
publicly available. The repository containing the source of the content is
intentionally not public, although the source for any individual page can be
downloaded by appending \`{/index.dj} to the URL (for example, here's
\link{source \label the source for this page}). You can similarly access the
changelog of any page by appending \`{/changelog} to the URL (as above, here's
\link{changelog \label the changelog for this page}).

\deflink nihil \target https://git.moonythm.dev/prescientmoon/nihil
